featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
For the construction of Ahmedabad, four Ahmeds had held the rope of the wall of the Kot, one of them was Hazrat Qazi Ahmed Jude, knowledgeable and punctual in Shariat, Fiqh, Hadith, Other Elm, he did not miss even a single prayer of five times a day, not even a Sunnah non-moveqda, he was the chief of Patan city. Justice had been the city Qazi. When Ahmedabad was settled, Sultan Ahmed Shah asked you to become the city Qazi of Ahmedabad but you preferred to live in Patan with simplicity and peace. Ahmedkhattu Ganj Baksh (Sarkhej) used to call you Khalifa-e-Azam.

Char Ahmed
1, Ahmed Khattu Ganjbakhsh-Sarkhej
2, Sultan Ahmedshah- Manekchok
3, Kazi Ahmed Malik -Kalupur Molki
pole
4, Kazi Ahmed Jood - Patan, Khalkpur

Not a single prayer of the four Ahmads, five times a day, was made qadha, and even the four rakats of Asr, Sunnah Gair Muqqida, were not made qaza.

featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
The Quran states in one of its verses:

"Vast-Eenu Bissabri Wasslah"

seek help through patience and prayers

It is clear that Namaz is a blessing from Allah for the convenience of a pure person. The example of 5 prayers is like having 5 holy canals at your door. Can you bathe in them five times a day and remain impure? Similarly, by bathing your mind in these canals, you wash away the soot and filth given by the world. Fear of Allah and His help help you in becoming a successful person.

featured_reviews.review_id:
Location: Patan Shareef

The kuffars beheadedHz. Bandagimiya Syed Khundmeer Rz. and 6 other shohdah and wanted to presentthem to Muzaffar (the then king) in exchange for a reward.

The 6 heads along withthe head of Hz. Bandagimiya Syed Khundmeer Rz. had offered 3 prayers (Asr, Maghriband Isha), seeing this sight the kuffars got frightened and removed the bonesand matter from the heads.

Bones and content of the skull of Hazrath Bandagimiya Syed Khundmir, Siddique e Vilayath RZ along with 5 other Shohdah.

This is the secondplace of burial of Hz. Bandagimiya Syed Khundmeer Rz.

The 5 other Shohdah whosePosht e Mubarak is buried here are:

1. Hz.Bandagimiya Syed Jalal Rz. S/o Hz. Bandagimiya Syed Khundmeer Rz.

2. Hz.Bandagimiya Syed Atan Rz. brother of Hz. Bandagimiya Syed Khundmeer Rz.

3. Hz.Bandagimiya Malik Hammad Rz. Uncle (mamu) of Hz. Bandagimiya Syed Khundmeer Rz.

4. Hz.Bandagimiya Malik Miyaji Rz. father in law of Hz. Bandagimiya Syed KhundmeerRz.

Also buried here is:

1. Hz.Bandagimiya Naseeruddin Mubarizul Mulk Rh. nana of Hz. Bandagimiya Syed KhundmeerRz.

2. Hz.Bandagimiya Malik Yousuf Rz. (Author of the book Prem Sangram)

3. Hz.Bandagimiya Malik Yaqoob Rz F/o Hz. Bandagimiya Malik Yousuf Rz.

4. Hz.Bandagimiya Syed Jalal Rh. S/o Syed Salamullah from the lineage of Hz.Bandagimiya Syed Shahabuddin Shahab ul haq Rz.

Hz. Bandagimiya MalikSharfuddin Rz. was also one of the martyrs whose head was cut off but his headand body were joined and buried at Patan Shareef by his relatives.

Hz. Bandagimiya KhanjiRz. is also one of the martyrs whose head was cut off.
